      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine lettura archivio dipendenza fornitore in [dcf]    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       let-arc-dcf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione marker di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se codice fornitore a zero                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-cod    =    zero
                     go to let-arc-dcf-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se codice dipendenza a spaces, solo se ri- *
      *              * chiesta di lettura specificamente di una dipen- *
      *              * denza                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-dpz    =    spaces and
                     w-let-arc-dcf-tle    =    "D"
                     go to let-arc-dcf-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se codice dipendenza a "*   ", solo se ri- *
      *              * chiesta di lettura specificamente di una dipen- *
      *              * denza                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-dcf-dpz    =    "*   " and
                     w-let-arc-dcf-tle    =    "D"
                     go to let-arc-dcf-450.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura per codice                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CODFNT    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-cod    to   rf-dcf-cod-fnt         .
           move      w-let-arc-dcf-dpz    to   rf-dcf-dpz-fnt         .
           move      "pgm/dcf/fls/ioc/obj/iofdcf"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-dcf                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to let-arc-dcf-400.
       let-arc-dcf-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bufferizzazione valori                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-dcf-rag-soc       to   w-let-arc-dcf-rag      .
           move      rf-dcf-rag-key       to   w-let-arc-dcf-rsu      .
           move      rf-dcf-via-dcf       to   w-let-arc-dcf-via      .
           move      rf-dcf-loc-dcf       to   w-let-arc-dcf-loc      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     let-arc-dcf-999.
       let-arc-dcf-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Azioni per record non trovato                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-let-arc-dcf-flg      .
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-dcf-rag      .
           go to     let-arc-dcf-600.
       let-arc-dcf-450.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione per codice dipendenza "*   "    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "Sia la sede che tutte le dipendenze     "
                                          to   w-let-arc-dcf-rag      .
           go to     let-arc-dcf-600.
       let-arc-dcf-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work area                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-rag      .
       let-arc-dcf-600.
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-rsu      .
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-via      .
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-dcf-loc      .
       let-arc-dcf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione descrizione riga ordine                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  :                                                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *    - Record di [bfr] relativo alla riga ordine fornitore  *
      *    *      a disposizione in rf-bfr                             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *    - Record di [dcf] relativo alla riga ordine fornitore  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output :                                                  *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *    - w-det-des-rig-des : Descrizione riga ordine          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-des-rig-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione valore in uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-det-des-rig-des      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del flag di estensione   *
      *              * alla descrizione                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bfr-des-ext       =    0
                     go to det-des-rig-100
           else if   rf-bfr-des-ext       =    1
                     go to det-des-rig-200
           else if   rf-bfr-des-ext       =    2
                     go to det-des-rig-300
           else if   rf-bfr-des-ext       =    3
                     go to det-des-rig-400.
       det-des-rig-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se nessuna estensione : bufferizzazione descri- *
      *              * zione contenuta nel record [bfr]                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bfr-des-rig       to   w-det-des-rig-des      .
           go to     det-des-rig-999.
       det-des-rig-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se estensione nel file [bfx]                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "NUMPRT    "         to   f-key                  .
           move      rf-bfr-num-prt       to   rf-bfx-num-prt         .
           move      rf-bfr-num-prg       to   rf-bfx-num-prg         .
           move      11                   to   rf-bfx-tip-rec         .
           move      "pgm/bfo/fls/ioc/obj/iofbfx"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-bfx                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     move  all '.'        to   rf-bfx-des-400         .
           move      rf-bfx-des-400       to   w-det-des-rig-des      .
           go to     det-des-rig-999.
       det-des-rig-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se estensione nel file [pdx]                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice lingua 'I  '                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-dcf-cod-lng       not  = "I  "
                     go to det-des-rig-350.
       det-des-rig-310.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura archivio [pdx]                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "TRCLNG"             to   f-key                  .
           move      01                   to   rf-pdx-tip-rec         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-pdx-cod-arc         .
           move      "I  "                to   rf-pdx-cod-lng         .
           move      rf-bfr-num-mag       to   rf-pdx-cod-num         .
           move      spaces               to   rf-pdx-for-mat         .
           move      01                   to   rf-pdx-num-prg         .
           move      "pgm/dcp/fls/ioc/obj/iofpdx"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-pdx                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     move  all "."        to   rf-pdx-des-pro         .
           move      rf-pdx-des-pro       to   w-det-des-rig-des      .
           go to     det-des-rig-999.
       det-des-rig-350.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice lingua diverso da 'I  '           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Tentativo di lettura file [pdx] per de- *
      *                      * scrizione in lingua estera              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "TRCLNG"             to   f-key                  .
           move      02                   to   rf-pdx-tip-rec         .
           move      zero                 to   rf-pdx-cod-arc         .
           move      rf-dcf-cod-lng       to   rf-pdx-cod-lng         .
           move      rf-bfr-num-mag       to   rf-pdx-cod-num         .
           move      spaces               to   rf-pdx-for-mat         .
           move      01                   to   rf-pdx-num-prg         .
           move      "pgm/dcp/fls/ioc/obj/iofpdx"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-pdx                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-des-rig-310.
           move      rf-pdx-des-pro       to   w-det-des-rig-des      .
           go to     det-des-rig-999.
       det-des-rig-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se estensione nel file [pdx] come estensione al *
      *              * file [aaf]                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "TRCLNG"             to   f-key                  .
           if        rf-bfr-tip-mag       =    01
                     move  13             to   rf-pdx-tip-rec
           else if   rf-bfr-tip-mag       =    03
                     move  33             to   rf-pdx-tip-rec
           else if   rf-bfr-tip-mag       =    04
                     move  43             to   rf-pdx-tip-rec         .
           move      rf-bfr-cod-arc       to   rf-pdx-cod-arc         .
           move      spaces               to   rf-pdx-cod-lng         .
           move      rf-bfr-num-mag       to   rf-pdx-cod-num         .
           move      rf-bfr-fda-pif       to   rf-pdx-for-mat         .
           move      01                   to   rf-pdx-num-prg         .
           move      "pgm/dcp/fls/ioc/obj/iofpdx"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-pdx                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to det-des-rig-310.
           move      rf-pdx-des-pro       to   w-det-des-rig-des      .
           go to     det-des-rig-999.
       det-des-rig-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine di conversione da altra valuta a valuta base      *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input  : w-cvs-vlt-sgl = Sigla dell'altra valuta          *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-dec = Numero decimali dell'altra valu- *
      *    *                          ta                               *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-tdc = Tipo di coefficiente dell'altra  *
      *    *                          valuta                           *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-cdc = Coefficiente di cambio dell'al-  *
      *    *                          tra valuta                       *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *          w-cvs-vlt-aav = Ammontare da convertire, espres- *
      *    *                          so nell'altra valuta             *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Output : w-cvs-vlt-avb = Ammontare convertito, espresso   *
      *    *                          nella valuta base                *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
